},{"pid":"d30e58a48765d2d616c18e4c8066bcf9a20adc4c","tid":1553972,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T21:57:38.000Z","msg":"你話我賣國都好,你唔係諗住只靠香港人可反攻全國<br />\n有今時今日的地步,都係靠外國比壓力,上面愛面子,加上比壓力同空位外國出手<br />\n當然啦,搵個英文撚出黎整口號最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a836133be63713877fc16c62f78dfb548ae5a71","tid":1553972,"uid":72597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"23df9d371f2c2419a930bee3bcee015c155f089d","tid":1553972,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T21:29:55.000Z","msg":"我起初成日以為時代革命係來自「時代精神」<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2597%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2Bstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=16cccad2\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E</a><br />\n<br />\n始終佢係讀哲學"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T22:01:15.000Z","msg":"唔係咩？"},{"pid":"d4735348d270646546f07b7565ad23725b7b5d99","tid":1553972,"uid":154793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T22:01:38.000Z","msg":"Reform Hong Kong.<br />\nRevolution for Generation."},{"pid":"8b7d97861c989c5a0a9b4b9bac327c0d57d067f4","tid":1553972,"uid":276911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T22:02:32.000Z","msg":"怪"},{"pid":"a091a1cf35ff5d9bfe24a8ce7cd8369eb63a04e3","tid":1553972,"uid":154793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T22:04:14.000Z","msg":"Shine for Hong Kong.<br />\nTime for reform."},{"pid":"81948e60a6b0fa022bf0385b507952ba452fff0c","tid":1553972,"uid":235174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a836133be63713877fc16c62f78dfb548ae5a71","tid":1553972,"uid":72597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"23df9d371f2c2419a930bee3bcee015c155f089d","tid":1553972,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T21:29:55.000Z","msg":"我起初成日以為時代革命係來自「時代精神」<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%2597%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2Bstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=16cccad2\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A3%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E</a><br />\n<br />\n始終佢係讀哲學"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T22:01:15.000Z","msg":"唔係咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T22:05:46.000Z","msg":"應該唔係，Zeitgeist解spirit of time，所有影響一個時代而非物質性既野既歷史觀<br />\n<br />\n但梁天琦原意係世代革新，本來aim年輕人，後來改進<br />\n<br />\n&quot;口號後半部份則是由原本的「世代革新」改進而成，並以「革命」一詞呼應本土民主前線的政治理念與組織定位。<br />\n在「時代革命」或「世代革命」的用詞選擇上，梁天琦最後決定以「時代革命」作為選舉口號，以強調革新與改變是不同年齡者都可以參與的行動，其只需要人們相信且擁抱自由，所以不會是「世代之爭」。他還指出，只要相信自由便能夠擁抱新的時代，並且應該去爭取、掌握命運。&quot;"},{"pid":"a3657aba34a6d7af160c2593489753203d02679b","tid":1553972,"uid":52849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T22:20:29.000Z","msg":"Free Hong Kong<br />\nRevolution of our time<br />\n<br />\nLiberate 解放通常有武裝起義嘅含意 解放同光復語意上其實有分別 唔明點解scmp會揀liberate<br />\n個人好唔喜歡個字隱含嘅衍生意思<br />\nFree係虛字 光復本身涵義好廣 用番個語意朦朧嘅free去襯托<br />\n時代革命係代表一整代人 破舊創造屬於我地嘅新時代<br />\n唔係立即屌你老母果隻now<br />\n<br />\nbbc呢個譯法其實幾靚幾傳神<br />\n除非堅持要為左做slogan將佢變啦"}]}